A train Monday morning rammed into a Volkswagen T4 bus at the ARENA crossing, in Oshodi, Lagos State. The Lagos State Traffic Management Authority (LASTMA) announced this on its Twitter handle on Monday morning. It said: “A train ran into a Volkswagen T4 bus at the ARENA crossing, pushing it to Oshodi U-bridge. Onlookers causing more harm than good. Men on ground, Necessary Agencies. “Traffic from Kara to Berger is building up fast, and moving INW Otedola bridge is getting steady approaching Olowopopo intersection.” https://t.co/D6BeQFThiL [9:03AM] #TrainAccident #AccidentUpdate #Oshodi
